---
title: Thai Style Veggie Curry with Jasmine Rice
description: When a dish this delicious is on the table in 35 minutes, you know you’ve struck gold. At HelloFresh, we believe that having a busy schedule should never stand in the way of cooking and enjoying great food. Packing a serious flavour punch, and bursting with good-for-you ingredients, this Thai veggie curry is guaranteed to become your favourite quick-fix recipe. Time might be your enemy, but this dish is your knight in shining armour!
